Standards-Version: 3.6.0

Package: mappero-geotagger
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Add location information to your pictures
 Mappero Geotagger is a graphical tool to add geolocation information to your
 pictures (JPEG, camera raw files and any other file supported by libexiv2).
 You can manually drag the pictures on a map, or correlate their timing with a
 GPX track generated by a GPS receiver.
Homepage: http://www.mardy.it/mappero-geotagger
